{"tid":2416270,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港電台大廈要強制檢測","createTime":"2021-02-21T02:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T03:58:22.000Z","uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb6267792d0466451474c51e6c3c0ef87ee3491","tid":2416270,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T02:05:39.000Z","msg":"節錄：<br />\n<br />\n香港電台繼早前一宗髮型師確診個案後，今再有一名助理編導確診，港台電視大廈或將納入強制檢測名單，現時大廈外已見檢測車。有港台員工透露，因擔憂大樓被突襲圍封令電視台「無嘢播」，<span class=\"gold\">部份員工已被要求在大樓內過夜和工作。</span><br />\n<br />\n員工斥管理層無對策 3直播節目暫停<br />\n ......<br />\n<br />\n此外，因應事件及港台員工須接受強制檢測，港台今明兩日共3個電視直播節目須暫停播放，包括《周末8點半》、《城市論壇》及《體壇無極限》，其餘節目則維持正常。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210220/Q7DOIRXHT5AEBMSJGQXJTGKFKE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210220%2FQ7DOIRXHT5AEBMSJGQXJTGKFKE%2F&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=3b249301\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210220%2FQ7DOIRXHT5AEBMSJGQXJTGKFKE%2F&h=4d199de5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210220/Q7DOIRXHT5AEBMSJGQXJTGKFKE/</a>"},{"pid":"c7bb21b2970343efd14366ec8c06c08c81519500","tid":2416270,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:58:22.000Z","msg":"Tvb測左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}